sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser (HTMX)
    participant D as Django View
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant T as Celery Worker

    Note over B,T: Execution detail page load (any status)

    B->>D: GET /flows/execution/<id>/
    D->>DB: FlowExecution + ExecutionStep.all()
    DB-->>D: execution, steps
    D-->>B: execution_detail.html<br/>(includes #live-status div with hx-get if PENDING/RUNNING)

    alt Status is PENDING or RUNNING
        Note over B,T: HTMX poll loop (every 3 s)

        loop Until terminal status returned
            B->>D: GET /flows/execution/<id>/live-status/ (HX-Request: true)
            D->>DB: FlowExecution (status, completed_at)<br/>ExecutionStep.all() ordered by step_index
            DB-->>D: current execution + steps
            D-->>B: execution_live_status.html partial<br/>(includes hx-trigger="every 3s" while PENDING/RUNNING)
            B->>B: HTMX swaps #live-status outerHTML
        end

        Note over B,T: Celery task updates DB concurrently

        T->>DB: ExecutionStep.transition(RUNNING)
        T->>DB: ExecutionStep.transition(COMPLETED)
        T->>DB: FlowExecution.transition(COMPLETED)

        B->>D: GET /flows/execution/<id>/live-status/ (next poll)
        D->>DB: FlowExecution (status=COMPLETED)<br/>ExecutionStep.all()
        DB-->>D: terminal execution + steps
        D-->>B: execution_live_status.html partial<br/>(NO hx-trigger — poll loop ends)
        B->>B: HTMX swaps #live-status outerHTML<br/>(static, no further requests)

    else Status is COMPLETED or FAILED
        Note over B: No hx-trigger rendered — zero poll requests
    end

    Note over B,T: prediction_running.html panel (dashboard)

    B->>D: GET /flows/prediction-status/<id>/ (existing HTMX poller)
    D->>DB: FlowExecution status check
    alt PENDING or RUNNING
        D->>DB: ExecutionStep.all()
        DB-->>D: steps (may be empty early on)
        D-->>B: prediction_running.html<br/>(step progress list + spinner)
    else COMPLETED
        D-->>B: prediction_result.html
    else FAILED
        D-->>B: prediction_error.html
    end
